sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as User
  participant T as TS Teams Adapter
  participant I as Entra ID
  participant R as Rust Agent Core
  participant K as Key Vault
  participant G as Microsoft Graph
  participant A as Audit Log

  U->>T: Trigger command requiring Graph access
  T-->>U: Show sign-in card
  U->>I: Authenticate + consent
  I-->>T: Auth code / token callback
  T->>R: OAuthCallback(AuthEnvelope: user_id, tenant_id, auth_context)
  R->>K: Store encrypted refresh token reference
  R->>A: write AuditEvent(action=oauth_callback, result=success)
  R-->>T: Ack

  T->>R: SendActivity(user command)
  R->>K: Retrieve token reference
  R->>I: Refresh access token when needed
  I-->>R: Access token
  R->>G: Graph request with delegated token
  G-->>R: Response
